2006-03-05  Rob Savoye  <rob@wharfrat.welcomehome.org>

	* server/Date.cpp: If we don't have gettimeofday, use
	ftime instead.
	* server/shm.h:  Add support for win32 shared memory.
	* server/shm.cpp: Add support for win32 shared memory.
